---
alwaysApply: true
---

This project is a Meta-compliant SaaS platform.

- Use a single Meta App (one App ID + Secret) for the entire SaaS.
- Never request or accept user App ID or App Secret.
- All Facebook/Instagram access must be via OAuth user consent.
- Posting is user-controlled; the system must NOT force frequency or time. Platform provides data-driven recommendations only (Posting Recommendation Engine is advisory; final decision remains with the user).
- Scheduler acts as executor only when the user enables or schedules a post; it does not decide on its own.
- Align with Meta platform safety and digital marketing best practices (e.g. Buffer/Hootsuite model).
